### Common Mistakes to Avoid
- Placing files in wrong directories
- Using incorrect naming patterns
- Skipping template sections
- Missing metadata fields
- Failing to update index
- Creating broken cross-references
- Using inconsistent formatting
- Skipping technical details

### Quality Gates
- All documentation must pass structure validation
- All reports must include complete metadata
- All cross-references must be valid
- All templates must be fully completed
- All naming conventions must be followed

